title: Aris Market Rule
author: wtyc
pages:
#- Aristopolis 
Market Rules
1:  You must reinforce you sign and chest to a group with Berge403 as a moderator for easy removal if your shop is ever in violation of any rules later in this manual or if your shop must be derelicted.
#- 2: You must put your shop in the area pertaining to the item your selling or buying as defined on the next page.  If you have any questions as to where your item shoud go, contact any of the people outlined at the end of this manual.
#- Shop Chest Areas:
Basic Building Materials
  Stone
  Brick
  Cobble 
  Torches
  Glass
  Dirt
Valuble Building Materials
  Lapiz
  Ores 
  Obsidian  
#- Mob Drops
  Bones
  Arrows
  Leather
  Zombie Armor Drops
  Gunpowder
  Ghast Tears
  (Anything else that drops from a mob)
Food:
  Anything that you can eat to regenerate your food bar.
#- Echanting:
  Potions of exp
  Glass Bottles
Potions
  Any type of potion
Potion Ingredientrs
  Any ingredient of a potion
#- Derelictions:
  If your shop is empty or can no longer sell or buy any of the item, your shop will be derelicted by a sign.  You will have 2 weeks to either refill your chest or remove it.  If it is not removed, you will lose your reinforcement materials.
#- Maket Consultants
